Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:28.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 虽然这般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:40.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回忆也会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被时间之沙掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:48.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而变得暧昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:55.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}说着「命运」这词是如此廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而与我一同开怀大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:05.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:10.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定会将自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐渐忘却在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}与你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也请留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:24.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成为无法集齐的拼图
